          <msContents>
            <summary>Tantric hymn dedicated to the great goddess Devī, which is a section of both the Ghaṭatantra and the Devīmāhātmya as presented in the Rudrayāmalatantra. Manuscript was folded into three sections to make it easy to carry for uses including recitation and rituals.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Devīsūktavarṇa</title>
              <title type="vernacular">देवीसूक्तवर्ण</title>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti śrīrudrayāmale ghaṭataṃtre devīmahātmye saptaśatikāyāṃ devīsuktavarṇanaṃ nāmatrayodaśo 'dhyāyaḥ // (f. 4v).</colophon>
            </msItem>
